{"tid":2454464,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"木村光希太辣！正面「薄紗又深V」大解放　曬雪白嫩腿","createTime":"2021-03-20T09:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T09:58:14.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f00619d4f7392fa469ae7e4645fa661334ff3be8","tid":2454464,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:09:13.000Z","msg":"「日劇天王」木村拓哉與工藤靜香18歲女兒木村光希跟20歲的姊姊木村心美也追隨爸媽腳步出道，可說是日本背景最強大的星二代之一，姊妹倆的追蹤人數都已破百萬，尤其是次女木村光希，從出道就踏入時尚圈，也受到各大精品青睞，接續成為寶格麗、Coach、FILA等品牌代言人，昨（19日）出席路易威登（LOUIS VUITTON）在日本東京的銀座並木通（Ginza Namiki-dori）專賣店，火辣深V讓人目不轉睛！<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/20/3073694-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F20%2F3073694-PH.jpg&h=4e680f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲木村光希出席LV展覽。（圖／翻攝自koki IG）<br />\n<br />\n木村光希身擁多項精品代言，最近卻經常受邀出席路易威登的活動，似乎品牌也有意想要延攬她入主。木村光希昨日出席專賣店開幕，身穿黑色深V短洋裝，胸前拼接透膚薄紗更引人遐想！一雙筆直美腿在鏡頭前更顯白皙，捨棄高跟鞋，穿上平底靴照樣走跳時尚場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/20/3073684-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F20%2F3073684-PH.jpg&h=d5cd4361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲木村光希日前現身東京LV專賣店開幕。（圖／翻攝自koki IG）<br />\n<br />\n不只路易威登（LOUIS VUITTON）頻頻招手，精品服飾 Valentino 已經搶先一步讓木村光希接下日本區代言人身份，最近拍攝的形象照出爐，木村光希換上該品牌所推出的刺繡鏤空襯衫，與各種修身洋裝，坐在地上擺出各種專業的姿勢，其中幾套短褲及短裙的造型，更將她一雙大長腿顯得更加纖細修長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/20/3073681-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F20%2F3073681-PH.jpg&h=a49aef23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲木村光希為Valentino日本區代言人。（圖／翻攝自koki IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/20/3073682-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F20%2F3073682-PH.jpg&h=3d788922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/maisonvalentino/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmaisonvalentino%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDAX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=5216ffab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/maisonvalentino/?utm_source=ig_embed</a>"},{"pid":"d50f01c1f46ae3c0b15b1adf298d048382861bef","tid":2454464,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:10:05.000Z","msg":"靚過彩十萬倍"},{"pid":"fa8fee46d94b0686359edb5d5e9f519bdd6433a8","tid":2454464,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d50f01c1f46ae3c0b15b1adf298d048382861bef","tid":2454464,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:10:05.000Z","msg":"靚過彩十萬倍"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:10:38.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n彩靚佢咁多"},{"pid":"18b4448bfd2ff68c54fbff1738d5926673532948","tid":2454464,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:11:11.000Z","msg":"都係中意家姐多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個身型比例好怪"},{"pid":"6c690b9e974ef42584f56cea7ea4fd6612bf9aa9","tid":2454464,"uid":48631,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PKTi1MX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPKTi1MX.png&h=6fa775b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1e32dffecc697ddb46181e8171c56ea30dabead","tid":2454464,"uid":58630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"成功靠父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e28ae87485a0981936354c43500cfeed3bb22e","tid":2454464,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d50f01c1f46a